liecycle hooks

1 - Mount
---------------
a) constructor
b) render
c) componentDidMount : called after component is render into the dom; perfect place to make ajax calls
               to get dat afrom the server


2 - Update
---------------
a) render
b) componentDidUpdate



3 - Unmount : component is removed from dom e.g deleting counter
-----------------
a) componentWillUnmount

